Startup Graduates

Startup graduates are companies who have gone through the EnterpriseWorks incubator and gone on to run successful companies. Since 2001, EnterpriseWorks has supported over 250 startups including receiving over $1.2 billion in venture capital funding.  Over 71% of the graduate companies remain in the state of Illinois and 66% remain in Champaign County.  From providing business consultations to SBIR assistance, EnterpriseWorks has mentored startups from the ground up.

The startup graduates listed below are companies that have gone through EnterpriseWorks and have now or graduated from the incubator. Please note that this is not a complete list of EnterpriseWorks Graduates. We are continuously updating this page, so please check back often.

View a list of the current companies at EnterpriseWorks here.
